# SCP Survivor Licensing Overview / 许可总览

This repository contains materials under more than one license. See `LICENSE-MAP.md` for the path-level scope. 本仓库包含适用不同许可证的材料；路径级范围见 `LICENSE-MAP.md`。

1. Independently authored software / 独立创作的软件
   Unless otherwise noted in `LICENSE-MAP.md`, source code, tests, scripts, configuration, and build tooling are licensed under the MIT License. The complete text is in `LICENSES/MIT.txt`.
   除 `LICENSE-MAP.md` 另有说明外，源代码、测试、脚本、配置和构建工具按 MIT License 提供；完整文本见 `LICENSES/MIT.txt`。
2. Creative content and SCP-derived material / 创意内容与 SCP 衍生材料
   Project-generated visual and audiovisual assets, game copy, narrative/design expression, and SCP-derived content are licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0. The complete text is in `LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-3.0.txt`; required attribution is in `ATTRIBUTION.md`.
   项目生成的视觉与视听素材、游戏文案、叙事/设计表达和 SCP 衍生内容按 Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 提供；完整文本见 `LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-3.0.txt`，必要署名见 `ATTRIBUTION.md`。
3. Third-party material / 第三方材料
   Third-party dependencies and any separately identified material remain under their own licenses. Their inclusion does not change those terms.
   第三方依赖和任何单独标明的材料继续适用其各自许可证，纳入本仓库不会改变这些条款。

Source and modification records for project-generated assets are listed in `docs/art/asset-register.md`. This selection does not warrant uniqueness, non-infringement, or clearance for a future commercial release. It preserves rights already granted for earlier MIT-licensed copies and is not legal advice.

项目生成素材的来源与修改记录见 `docs/art/asset-register.md`。本次许可选择不构成对唯一性、不侵权或未来商业发行权利完备的保证；也不撤回既有 MIT 许可副本已经获得的权利，且不构成法律意见。
